@drchatterjee joined me on a past episode of The Doctor’s Farmacy to explain his 3F approach that you practice before you reach for a treat or junk food, which is designed to help you dig deep and figure out WHY it is that you want to eat. Because it’s only after you build awareness, that you’ll be able to create a non-food behavior to help you cope with your emotions.⁣
⁣
You can listen to the full episode, “The Secret To Losing Weight And Feeling Great”, on your favorite podcast app.⁣

